extRef="OneD" unitRef="INRPerShare" decimals="INF">-19.77</in-bse-fin:DilutedEarningsLossPerShareFromContinuingOperations><in-bse-fin:BasicEarningsLossPerShareFromDiscontinuedOperations contextRef="OneD" unitRef="INRPerShare" decimals="INF">0</in-bse-fin:BasicEarningsLossPerShareFromDiscontinuedOperations><in-bse-fin:DilutedEarningsLossPerShareFromDiscontinuedOperations contextRef="OneD" unitRef="INRPerShare" decimals="INF">0</in-bse-fin:DilutedEarningsLossPerShareFromDiscontinuedOperations><in-bse-fin:BasicEarningsLossPerShareFromContinuingAndDiscontinuedOperations contextRef="OneD" unitRef="INRPerShare" decimals="INF">-19.77</in-bse-fin:BasicEarningsLossPerShareFromContinuingAndDiscontinuedOperations><in-bse-fin:DilutedEarningsLossPerShareFromContinuingAndDiscontinuedOperations contextRef="OneD" unitRef="INRPerShare" decimals="INF">-19.77</in-bse-fin:DilutedEarningsLossPerShareFromContinuingAndDiscontinuedOperations><in-bse-fin:DebtEquityRatio contextRef="OneD" unitRef="pure" decimals="INF">0.0033</in-bse-fin:DebtEquityRatio><in-bse-fin:DebtServiceCoverageRatio contextRef="OneD" unitRef="pure" decimals="INF">-0.049</in-bse-fin:DebtServiceCoverageRatio><in-bse-fin:InterestServiceCoverageRatio contextRef="OneD" unitRef="pure" decimals="INF">-0.0633</in-bse-fin:InterestServiceCoverageRatio><in-bse-fin:DisclosureOfNotesOnFinancialResultsExplanatoryTextBlock contextRef="OneD">1.The above results have been prepared in accordance with IND AS, duly reviewed and recommended by Audit Committee were approved by the Board of Directors at the Meeting held on 04.08.2022. &lt;BR&gt; 
2.Last tranche of Non-convertible secured Debentures of Rs. 100 crores were redeemed on 18.05.2022. &lt;BR&gt; 
3.Export packing credit outstanding as on 30.06.2022 is Rs 7334 Lakhs. &lt;BR&gt; 
4.Exemption has been granted by Ministry of Corporate Affairs (MCA) from publishing segment-wise information. &lt;BR&gt; 
5.As per CCEA approval dtd 8th September 2021, M/s Vignyan Industries Ltd, a subsidiary of BEML is under Voluntary Liquidation. Movable assets have been disposed off and disposal of immovable assets is in progress. &lt;BR&gt; 
6.For demerger of surplus assets of BEML, a wholly owned subsidiary- BEML Land Assets Limited (BLAL), was incorporated on 15-07-2021. Scheme of arrangement for demerger of surplus/non-core assets from BEML to BLAL has been cleared by Stock Exchanges viz., BSE &amp; NSE. The Scheme of arrangement of demerger has also been approved by Shareholders and Creditors (both Secured and Un-secured) of BEML. The approval of Scheme of Arrangement of demerger is under process in line with the guidelines of Ministry of Corporate Affairs, Govt. of India. &lt;BR&gt; 
7.As required under SEBI regulations, a limited review of the above financials was conducted  by the Statutory Auditors and the Limited Review Report as duly placed before the aforesaid meeting of the Board is enclosed. &lt;BR&gt; 
8.The previous period figures have been regrouped and reclassified wherever necessary to make them comparable with the current period figures.  &lt;BR&gt; 
9.The figures of quarter ended 31st March 2022 are the balancing figures between the audited figures of full financial year ended 31st March 2022 and published figures upto 31st December 2021. &lt;BR&gt; 
10.Revenue from Operation includes Revenue from Sale of products and Services Rs 66320 Lakhs (PY Rs 45100 Lakhs) and Other operating revenue of Rs 598 Lakhs  (PY Rs 1619 Lakhs). </in-bse-fin:DisclosureOfNotesOnFinancialResultsExplanatoryTextBlock><in-bse-fin:DescriptionOfOtherExpenses contextRef="OneExpenses1D">Other Expenses</in-bse-fin:DescriptionOfOtherExpenses><in-bse-fin:OtherExpenses contextRef="OneExpenses1D" unitRef="INR" decimals="-5">1305000000</in-bse-fin:OtherExpenses><in-bse-fin:DescriptionOfItemThatWillNotBeReclassifiedToProfitAndLoss contextRef="D_ItemsThatWillNotBeReclassifiedToProfitAndLoss11">Other Comprehensive income</in-bse-fin:DescriptionOfItemThatWillNotBeReclassifiedToProfitAndLoss><in-bse-fin:AmountOfItemThatWillNotBeReclassifiedToProfitAndLoss contextRef="D_ItemsThatWillNotBeReclassifiedToProfitAndLoss11" unitRef="INR" decimals="-5">-235200000</in-bse-fin:AmountOfItemThatWillNotBeReclassifiedToProfitAndLoss><in-bse-fin:AmountOfItemThatWillNotBeReclassifiedToProfitAndLoss contextRef="OneD" unitRef="INR" decimals="-5">-235200000</in-bse-fin:AmountOfItemThatWillNotBeReclassifiedToProfitAndLoss><in-bse-fin:IncomeTaxRelatingToItmesThatWillNotBeReclassifiedToProfitOrLoss contextRef="OneD" unitRef="INR" decimals="-5">0</in-bse-fin:IncomeTaxRelatingToItmesThatWillNotBeReclassifiedToProfitOrLoss><in-bse-fin:IncomeTaxRelatingToItmesThatWillBeReclassifiedToProfitOrLoss contextRef="OneD" unitRef="INR" decimals="-5">0</in-bse-fin:IncomeTaxRelatingToItmesThatWillBeReclassifiedToProfitOrLoss></xbrli:xbrl>
